{
  "id": "5cb1ac5b25f1770017138d63",
  "title": "コミュニケーションのメンタルモデル変遷",
  "created": 1555147872,
  "updated": 1590566719,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5cb1ac5b25f1770017138d63",
      "text": "コミュニケーションのメンタルモデル変遷",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555147872,
      "updated": 1555147876
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1b796aff09e0000793e29",
      "text": "[コミュニケーション]の[メンタルモデル]変遷",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555150742,
      "updated": 1555150748
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1b79daff09e0000793e2a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555150749,
      "updated": 1555150749
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1af9aaff09e0000793e21",
      "text": "音声会話",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148699,
      "updated": 1555148705
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1ac64aff09e00008eaccb",
      "text": "\t少数の人に話しかける",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555147877,
      "updated": 1555148705
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1ac88aff09e00008eaccd",
      "text": "\t大勢の人に呼びかける",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555147913,
      "updated": 1555148706
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1ac8eaff09e00008eacce",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555147919,
      "updated": 1555147919
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1ace0aff09e00008eaccf",
      "text": "書き言葉についても同じ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148004,
      "updated": 1555148006
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1ace6aff09e00008eacd0",
      "text": "\tひとりの人に手紙を送る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148006,
      "updated": 1555148709
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1ac88aff09e00008eaccc",
      "text": "\t大勢に印刷物を配布する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555147912,
      "updated": 1555148710
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1acfbaff09e00008eacd2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148028,
      "updated": 1555148028
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1ad25aff09e00008eacd6",
      "text": "大勢に聞かれる・読まれる機会は権威と紐づいていた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148073,
      "updated": 1555148723
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1ad33aff09e00008eacd8",
      "text": "\t新聞に投書",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148083,
      "updated": 1555148724
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1ad25aff09e00008eacd7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148073,
      "updated": 1555148073
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1acfcaff09e00008eacd3",
      "text": "インターネット",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148028,
      "updated": 1555148041
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1ad09aff09e00008eacd4",
      "text": "\t[書き言葉]の流通コストを下げた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148042,
      "updated": 1555149311
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1ad14aff09e00008eacd5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148052,
      "updated": 1555148052
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1acfbaff09e00008eacd1",
      "text": "書き言葉に対してだけ少し早く「大勢に書き言葉を届けること」がコモディティ化した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148028,
      "updated": 1555148785
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1aff1aff09e0000793e23",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148785,
      "updated": 1555148785
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1b0d0aff09e0000793e24",
      "text": "コストが下がったことによって、強い意思がなくても行われる状態が発生した。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555149008,
      "updated": 1555149022
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1b0deaff09e0000793e25",
      "text": "つまり「特に誰かに伝えたいわけではない」「読者を想定しない」書き言葉の発信が行われるようになった。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555149022,
      "updated": 1555149051
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb68b64aff09e0000f3fc3e",
      "text": "[受け手を想定しない発話]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555467109,
      "updated": 1555467113
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1b0fbaff09e0000793e26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555149051,
      "updated": 1555149051
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1b0fbaff09e0000793e27",
      "text": "2019年現在、20歳の人はWindows98ブームの後に生まれた人",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555149051,
      "updated": 1555149419
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1b26baff09e0000793e28",
      "text": "20歳〜60歳の間にこの過渡期が挟まっているため世代間でメンタルモデルの差がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555149419,
      "updated": 1555150735
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb1afc3aff09e0000793e22",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555148740,
      "updated": 1555148740
    },
    {
      "id": "5ece1e2eaff09e0000ce8008",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1590566446,
      "updated": 1590566678
    },
    {
      "id": "5ece1f16aff09e0000ce800a",
      "text": "\t[世代間のコミュニケーションの違い、の補足 - ところてん - Medium https://medium.com/@tokoroten/%E4%B8%96%E4%BB%A3%E9%96%93%E3%81%AE%E3%82%B3%E3%83%9F%E3%83%A5%E3%83%8B%E3%82%B1%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%B3%E3%81%AE%E9%81%95%E3%81%84-%E3%81%AE%E8%A3%9C%E8%B6%B3-f69d544b2860]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1590566678,
      "updated": 1590566690
    },
    {
      "id": "5ece1f22aff09e0000ce800b",
      "text": " \t[世代間のコミュニケーションの違い]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1590566690,
      "updated": 1590566701
    },
    {
      "id": "5ece1f16aff09e0000ce8009",
      "text": "\t[発言に意図がある前提]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1590566678,
      "updated": 1590566718
    }
  ]
}